   20: -module(groups_12_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -compile(export_all).
   23: 
   24: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   25: 
   26: %%====================================================================
   27: %% COMMON TEST CALLBACK FUNCTIONS
   28: %%====================================================================
   29: 
   30: suite() ->
   31:     [{timetrap,{minutes,1}}].
   32: 
   33: groups() ->
   34:     [
   35:       {test_group_1a, [shuffle], [testcase_1a,testcase_1b,testcase_1c]},
   36: 
   37:       {test_group_1b, [parallel], [testcase_1a,testcase_1b]},
   38: 
   39:       {test_group_2, [parallel], [testcase_2a,
   40: 
   41: 				  {test_group_3, [{repeat,2}],
   42: 				   [testcase_3a, testcase_3b]},
   43: 
   44: 				  testcase_2b]},
   45: 
   46:       {test_group_4, [{test_group_5, [parallel], [testcase_5a,
   47: 
   48: 						  {group, test_group_6},
   49: 
   50: 						  testcase_5b]}]},
   51: 
   52:       {test_group_6, [parallel], [{group, test_group_7},
   53: 				  {group, test_group_8}]},
   54: 
   55:       {test_group_7, [sequence], [testcase_7a,testcase_7b]},
   56: 
   57:       {test_group_8, [shuffle,sequence], [testcase_8a,testcase_8b]}
   58:      ].
   59: 
   60: all() ->
   61:     [{group, test_group_1a},
   62:      {group, test_group_1b},
   63:      testcase_1,
   64:      testcase_2,
   65:      {group, test_group_2},
   66:      testcase_3,
   67:      {group, test_group_4}].
   68: 
   69: %% this func only for internal test purposes
   70: grs_and_tcs() ->
   71:     {[
   72:       test_group_1a, test_group_1b,
   73:       test_group_2, test_group_3,
   74:       test_group_4, test_group_5,
   75:       test_group_6, test_group_7,
   76:       test_group_8
   77:      ],
   78:      [
   79:       testcase_1a, testcase_1b, testcase_1c,
   80:       testcase_1,
   81:       testcase_2,
   82:       testcase_2a, testcase_2b,
   83:       testcase_3a, testcase_3b,
   84:       testcase_3,
   85:       testcase_5a, testcase_5b,
   86:       testcase_7a, testcase_7b,
   87:       testcase_8a, testcase_8b
   88:      ]}.
   89: 
   90: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   91: %% Suite Configuration
   92: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   93: 
   94: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   95:     [{suite,init}|Config].
   96: 
   97: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   98:     init = ?config(suite,Config).
   99: 
  100: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  101: %% Group Configuration
  102: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  103: 
  104: init_per_group(Group, Config) ->
  105:     Cmt =
  106: 	case {Group,?config(tc_group_properties,Config)} of
  107: 	    {test_group_1a,[{shuffle,S},{name,test_group_1a}]} ->
  108: 		io_lib:format("shuffled, ~w", [S]);
  109: 	    {test_group_1b,[{name,test_group_1b},parallel]} -> "parallel";
  110: 	    {test_group_2,[{name,test_group_2},parallel]} -> "parallel";
  111: 	    {test_group_3,[{name,test_group_3},{repeat,2}]} -> "repeat 2";
  112: 	    {test_group_3,[{name,test_group_3}]} -> "repeat 1";
  113: 	    {test_group_4,[{name,test_group_4}]} -> ok;
  114: 	    {test_group_5,[{name,test_group_5},parallel]} -> "parallel";
  115: 	    {test_group_6,[{name,test_group_6},parallel]} -> "parallel";
  116: 	    {test_group_7,[{name,test_group_7},sequence]} -> "sequence";
  117: 	    {test_group_8,[{shuffle,_},{name,test_group_8},sequence]} ->
  118: 		"shuffle & sequence"
  119: 	end,
  120:     {Grs,_} = grs_and_tcs(),
  121:     case lists:member(Group, Grs) of
  122: 	true ->
  123: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  124: 	    ct:comment(io_lib:format("~w, ~s", [Group,Cmt])),
  125: 	    [{Group,Group} | Config];
  126: 	false ->
  127: 	    ct:fail({bad_group,Group})
  128:     end.
  129: 
  130: end_per_group(Group, Config) ->
  131:     {Grs,_} = grs_and_tcs(),
  132:     case lists:member(Group, Grs) of
  133: 	true ->
  134: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  135: 	    Group = ?config(Group,Config),
  136: 	    ok;
  137: 	false ->
  138: 	    ct:fail({bad_group,Group})
  139:     end.
  140: 
  141: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  142: %% Testcase Configuration
  143: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  144: 
  145: init_per_testcase(TestCase, Config) ->
  146:     {_,TCs} = grs_and_tcs(),
  147:     case lists:member(TestCase, TCs) of
  148: 	true ->
  149: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  150: 	    [{TestCase,TestCase} | Config];
  151: 	false ->
  152: 	    ct:fail({unknown_testcase,TestCase})
  153:     end.
  154: 
  155: end_per_testcase(TestCase, Config) ->
  156:     {_,TCs} = grs_and_tcs(),
  157:     case lists:member(TestCase, TCs) of
  158: 	true ->
  159: 	    init = ?config(suite,Config),
  160: 	    TestCase = ?config(TestCase,Config),
  161: 	    ok;
  162: 	false ->
  163: 	    ct:fail({unknown_testcase,TestCase})
  164:     end.
  165:

  171: testcase_1a() ->
  172:     [].
  173: testcase_1a(Config) ->
  174:     init = ?config(suite,Config),
  175:     case ?config(test_group_1a,Config) of
  176: 	test_group_1a -> ok;
  177: 	_ ->
  178: 	    case ?config(test_group_1b,Config) of
  179: 		test_group_1b -> ok;
  180: 		_ -> ct:fail(no_group_data)
  181: 	    end
  182:     end,

  184:     ok.
